description: This file defines the Attendee entity class for the event management backend, including JPA annotations for ORM mapping, fields for attendee details, constructors, and accessor methods.

classes.name: Attendee
classes.description: Entity class representing an attendee for an event, with fields for id, name, email, and associated event, along with relevant JPA annotations and constructors.

methods.name: Attendee
methods.description: Default constructor for initializing an empty Attendee object.

methods.name: Attendee
methods.description: Constructor initializing an Attendee with name, email, and associated event.

methods.description: Returns the unique identifier of the attendee.

methods.name: setId
methods.description: Sets the unique identifier for the attendee.
